modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fid1665702811966.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fid1665702811966.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fid1665702811966.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fid1665702811966\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Trigger Editor for Menus\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Trigger editor for Menus enables you to edit the ProcScript for drop-down menus and menu items. It features syntax highlighting, syntax checking, keyword completion, and context-sensitive help for ProcScript keywords.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fid1665702811966__p_d7100e1_d7101e1_d7102e1\">Menu items can have an option trigger and preDisplay\n         trigger. Drop-down menus can have a preDisplay trigger. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eji1665703130687.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eji1665703130687.html\" title=\"Trigger for handling the processing that should occur after a menu item is selected.\">trigger option</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ckm1665702665911.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ckm1665702665911.html\" title=\"System trigger that is executed before a menu or menu item is displayed.\">trigger preDisplay</a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fid1665702811966__p_d7103e1_d7104e1_d7105e1\">The Trigger Editor consists of the following resizable areas:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fid1665702811966__li_d3509e1_d3510e1_d3511e1\">Structure—view hierarchical structure of the current menu object.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fid1665702811966__li_d3512e1_d3513e1_d3514e1\">Script Editor—view and edit ProcScript in the current trigger.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fid1665702811966__li_d3515e1_d3516e1_d3517e1\">Tags—view and navigate to tagged triggers that match search criteria (when you use <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Find</span>) or contain errors (after a syntax check).\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fid1665702811966__li_d3518e1_d3519e1_d3520e1\">Triggers—view and navigate to the Option and Predisplay triggers of the current menu option. The icon beside each trigger indicates whether the trigger contains content or not.\n <div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fid1665702811966__table_d608e1_d609e1_d610e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Trigger Icons</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fid1665702811966__table_d608e1_d609e1_d610e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fid1665702811966__table_d608e1_d609e1_d610e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Meaning</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d608e1_d609e1_d610e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_w80ab1b7b5b7b1b3b7b1b1b1_w81ab1b7b5b7b1b3b7b1b1_w82ab1b7b5b7b1b3b7b1_w83ab1b7b5b7b1b3b7_w84ab1b7b5b7b1b3_w85ab1b7b5b7b1_w86ab1b7b5b7_w87ab1b7b5_w88ab1b7_w89ab1\">\n<img alt=\"No triggers\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_trglck.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d608e1_d609e1_d610e1__entry__2\">There are no triggers for the selected menu\n                           object. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d608e1_d609e1_d610e1__entry__1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_w90ab1b7b5b7b1b3b7b3b1b1b1_w91ab1b7b5b7b1b3b7b3b1b1_w92ab1b7b5b7b1b3b7b3b1_w93ab1b7b5b7b1b3b7b3_w94ab1b7b5b7b1b3b7_w95ab1b7b5b7b1b3_w96ab1b7b5b7b1_w97ab1b7b5b7_w98ab1b7b5_w99ab1b7_w100ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Empty trigger\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_trgemp.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d608e1_d609e1_d610e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The trigger is empty.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d608e1_d609e1_d610e1__entry__1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_w101ab1b7b5b7b1b3b7b5b1b1b1_w102ab1b7b5b7b1b3b7b5b1b1_w103ab1b7b5b7b1b3b7b5b1_w104ab1b7b5b7b1b3b7b5_w105ab1b7b5b7b1b3b7_w106ab1b7b5b7b1b3_w107ab1b7b5b7b1_w108ab1b7b5b7_w109ab1b7b5_w110ab1b7_w111ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Trigger contains code\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_trgstd.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d608e1_d609e1_d610e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The trigger contains code.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fid1665702811966__section_gl2_j2g_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d946907e187\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fid1665702811966__p_d7109e1_d7110e1_d7111e1\">It is only possible to define triggers for menu\n            options.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"fid1665702811966__ul_vnm_l2g_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fid1665702811966__li_d3521e1_d3522e1_d3523e1\">To complete a keyword: <ul class=\"ul\" id=\"fid1665702811966__ul_wnm_l2g_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fid1665702811966__li_d3524e1_d3525e1_d3526e1\">Start typing a ProcScript keyword (such as a\n                     statement, function, precompiler directive, or compiler-time constant) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fid1665702811966__li_d3527e1_d3528e1_d3529e1\">Press <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab</span> until the\n                     keyword you want to use is inserted. <p class=\"p\" id=\"fid1665702811966__p_d7112e1_d7113e1_d7114e1\">For\n                        example, when you type <code class=\"ph codeph\">sel</code> followed by\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab</span>, the keyword <code class=\"ph codeph\">selectcase</code> is\n                        displayed. Press <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab</span> again and\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">selectdb</span> is displayed. After the complete keyword list\n                        is displayed, the list is exited and a standard tab action is performed.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fid1665702811966__li_d3530e1_d3531e1_d3532e1\">To move backward in the list, press\n                        <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Shift</span>+<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab</span>. </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fid1665702811966__li_d3533e1_d3534e1_d3535e1\">To get help about a ProcScript keyword, position the\n               cursor on a ProcScript keyword and press <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">F1</span>.  <p class=\"p\" id=\"fid1665702811966__p_d7118e1_d7119e1_d7120e1\">The appropriate reference description is displayed\n                  in the Uniface Library.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fid1665702811966__section_m5j_42g_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d946907e250\">Toolbar</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><div class=\"dataTables_wrapper no-footer\" id=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1_wrapper\"><div class=\"dataTables_filter\" id=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1_filter\"><label>Search:<input aria-controls=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1\" class=\"\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"search\"/></label></div><div class=\"zDocsFilterTableDiv false\"><button aria-expanded=\"fal