head\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"height: 0px;\"><th aria-controls=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1\" aria-label=\"Icon : activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: 0px; width: 47.8125px;\"><div class=\"dataTables_sizing\" style=\"height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\">Icon </div></th><th aria-controls=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1\" aria-label=\"Description : activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: 0px; width: 610.188px;\"><div class=\"dataTables_sizing\" style=\"height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\">Description </div></th></tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Open icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_ftp_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Open icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_gtp_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_apsopen.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Open another menu. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Save icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_htp_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Save icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_itp_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u_store.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Save the current component. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Duplicate object icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_jtp_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Duplicate object icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_ktp_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_cmpduplicate.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Make a copy of the current component.</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Add tag icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_ltp_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Add tag icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_mtp_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_tagstd.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Add manual tag for current trigger. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Compile all objects\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_ntp_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Compile all objects\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_otp_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_checkmod.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Check syntax of modified triggers. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Compile modified object\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_ptp_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Compile modified object\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_qtp_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_checkall.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Check syntax of all triggers. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Undo edit\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_rtp_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Undo edit\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_stp_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u_fieldundo.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Ctrl</span>+<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Z</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Undo the most recent ProcScript edit, up to a\n                        maximum of 16 actions. <p class=\"p\">It is not possible to undo typing that is\n                           immediately followed by a carriage return.</p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Redo edit\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_ttp_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Redo edit\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_utp_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u_fieldredo.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Ctrl</span>+<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Y</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Redo the most recently undone edit. <p class=\"p\">You\n                           cannot undo an action that has been redone.</p>\n</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Tabify icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_vtp_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Tabify icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_wtp_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_tabify.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Replace spaces by tabs in selected text. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Untabify icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_xtp_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Untabify icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_ytp_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_untabify.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Replace tabs by spaces in the selected text.\n                     </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Increase indent icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_ztp_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Increase indent icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_a5p_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_incrindent.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Add tab of each line in selected text. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Decrease indent\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_b5p_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Decrease indent\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_c5p_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_decrindent.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Remove first tab of each line in selected text. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Convert to uppercase icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_d5p_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Convert to uppercase icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_e5p_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_uppercase.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Convert the selected text to uppercase. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Convert to lowercase icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_f5p_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Convert to lowercase icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_g5p_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_lowercase.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Convert the selected text to lowercase. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Format ProcScript icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_h5p_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Format ProcScript icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_i5p_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_cmpformatproc.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Format the ProcScript, adding indentation for\n                        readability. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Convert to comment icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_j5p_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Convert to comment icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_k5p_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_cmpcomment.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Convert the selected ProcScript to comments. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Uncomment icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_l5p_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Uncomment icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_m5p_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_cmpuncomment.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Convert the selected comments to ProcScript\n                        code. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Find\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_n5p_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Find\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_o5p_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u_find24.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Search the current ProcScript for a string. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"FInd next in ProcScript\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_p5p_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"FInd next in ProcScript\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_q5p_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_cmpfindnxtprc.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Find the next occurrence of the search string. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Find and replace icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_r5p_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Find and replace icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_s5p_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u_findrepl24.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Find a search string and replace it with\n                        another string. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Find and replace icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_t5p_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Find and replace icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_u5p_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_cmpfindcmp.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Find ProcScript in the component. </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" data-search=\"Quick zoom icon\" id=\"fid1665702811966__fig_v5p_p2g_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Quick zoom icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fid1665702811966__image_w5p_p2g_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u8_quickzoom.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fid1665702811966__table_d611e1_d612e1_d613e1__entry__2\">Open the in a separate window for editing.\n                     </td>\n</tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"dataTables_scrollFoot\" style=\"overflow: hidden; border: 0px; width: 100%;\"><div class=\"dataTables_scrollFootInner\"><table class=\"table dataTable no-footer\" count-columns=\"2\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;\"><tfoot></tfoot></table></div></div></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jcx1707814817129.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ProcScript Syntax</a><p>ProcScript provides high-level statements, functions, expressions, and operators that enable you to efficiently manipulate data and script application behavior. It is a powerful language that condenses complex processing into single commands.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8419845\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8419845\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Trigger Editor for Menus Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Trigger Editor for Menus The Trigger editor for Menus enables you to edit the ProcScript for drop-down menus and menu items. It features syntax highlighting, syntax checking, keyword completion, and context-sensitive help for ProcScript keywords. Menu items can have an option trigger and preDisplay trigger. Drop-down menus can have a preDisplay trigger. For more information, see trigger option and trigger preDisplay The Trigger Editor consists of the following resizable areas: Structure—view hierarchical structure of the current menu object. Script Editor—view and edit ProcScript in the current trigger. Tags—view and navigate to tagged triggers that match search criteria (when you use Find ) or contain errors (after a syntax check). Triggers—view and navigate to the Option and Predisplay triggers of the current menu option. The icon beside each trigger indicates whether the trigger contains content or not. Table 1. Trigger Icons Icon Meaning There are no triggers for the selected menu object. The trigger is empty. The trigger contains code. How to It is only possible to define triggers for menu options. To complete a keyword: Start typing a ProcScript keyword (such as a statement, function, precompiler directive, or compiler-time constant) Press Tab until the keyword you want to use is inserted. For example, when you type sel followed by Tab , the keyword selectcase is displayed. Press Tab again and selectdb is displayed. After the complete keyword list is displayed, the list is exited and a standard tab action is performed. To move backward in the list, press Shift + Tab . To get help about a ProcScript keyword, position the cursor on a ProcScript keyword and press F1 . The appropriate reference description is displayed in the Uniface Library. Toolbar Search: Column Icon Description Filter results... 22 rows found Export to Excel Export to CSV Table 2. ProcScript Editor Toolbar Icon Description Filter 22 rows found Filter 22 rows found Icon Description Open another menu. Save the current component. Make a copy of the current component. Add manual tag for current trigger. Check syntax of modified triggers. Check syntax of all triggers. Ctrl + Z Undo the most recent ProcScript edit, up to a maximum of 16 actions. It is not possible to undo typing that is immediately followed by a carriage return. Ctrl + Y Redo the most recently undone edit. You cannot undo an action that has been redone. Replace spaces by tabs in selected text. Replace tabs by spaces in the selected text. Add tab of each line in selected text. Remove first tab of each line in selected text. Convert the selected text to uppercase. Convert the selected text to lowercase. Format the ProcScript, adding indentation for readability. Convert the selected ProcScript to comments. Convert the selected comments to ProcScript code. Search the current ProcScript for a string. Find the next occurrence of the search string. Find a search string and replace it with another string. Find ProcScript in the component. Open the in a separate window for editing. Related Links ProcScript Syntax ProcScript provides high-level statements, functions, expressions, and operators that enable you to efficiently manipulate data and script application behavior. It is a powerful language that condenses complex processing into single commands. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}